## 3. Scope Check + "Simply the Hadacard"
✅ Exact match to message.
- "remove the scenes that proceed that with simply the Hadacard": Hadacard will be made (even more) self-contained and scene-free internally. No preceding bubble/finalCard/egift logic lives in it (already cleaned in prior; we excise any remaining). It becomes the pure, reusable "letter" unit that can be dropped simply anywhere as centerpiece (home already does this; future gift flows can too without complex wrapper scenes). The component itself will have no "proceeding scenes".
- "add a mode to the hadacard to animate it open it up... more center piece before the orchid": New `open?: boolean` (default true for zero-break) + internal or controlled state. When closed: elegant sealed/letter-front face (holo retained, name + "for you" + subtle seal hint, tap-to-open). Transition: smooth pretty wide unfold (3d flap, content reveal cascade, breathing room, aspect relaxation or generous layout for "wide open letter" aesthetic). When open: the current beautiful letter content, enhanced for centerpiece (larger breathing message, polished spacing, still fully interactive pointer holo). This positions Hadacard as the emotional "letter opening" moment immediately preceding the living orchid reveal.
- "plan out a refactor that is clean and functional for future reuse": Full IIPS pass — tiny pure helpers, props resolved as () => getters, signals only where live, onCleanup, no dupe types, comments affectionate + precise, barrel clean.
- "port all types into src/types [from] the component to keep it clean": Local CardMeta + ThreeCardProps removed from Hadacard.tsx. New `HadacardProps` (and any refined) added to web/src/types/index.ts as canonical. Component imports from '@/types'.
- "do similar with generalizable src/utils": `splitToLetterBlocks` (the only private util with animation semantics) extracted to new `web/src/utils/letters.ts` (simple typed name). Component + any future letter/anim consumers import it. Barrel? Not needed yet; direct import ok for $ kind.
- "it should open up wide animate smooth and pretty": Core deliverable of the mode. Use CSS transitions + new keyframes (letterUnfold, cardOpen, flap etc) + staged Solid signals for content (profile first, then titles, then body message with gentle delays). Holo layers remain live during/after. Touch/pointer friendly. Defaults + existing usage 100% visually preserved when open=true.
- Future reuse: props are all optional with affectionate defaults; open mode controllable (e.g. parent can drive "open on mount with delay" or user gesture); no hard deps on routes/configs.

